<title>INN NUAM, INN THLUACHUAK CH494</title>
<key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawi Khrih umnak inn cu inn nuam a si, Dawtnak, remnak zungzal in a
 leng, Hi innchungkhar thluachuah na pekmi nih na min sunhlawinak a
 chuahpi tawn.

[C1]
   Bawi Khrih a umnak inn cu (nak inn cu) Inn nuam, inn thluachuak a
   si, Bawi Khrih muihmai a cung, (hmai a cuang zungzal,) Bawi Khrih lungput
   a leng (Bawi Khrih lungput a leng) Khrihfa nunning fiang tein a lang.
   (nunning fiang tein a lang).

[V2]
 Bawi Khrih ukmi inn cu inn nuam a si, Satan hlennak nih a hrawk kho
 lo, Khrihfabu caah hrih le hram a si i zohchunh awk ca zongah a si.

[C2]
   Bawi Khrih a umnak inn cu (nak inn cu) Inn nuam, inn thluachuak a
   si, Bawi Khrih muihmai a cung, (hmai a cuang zungzal,) Bawi Khrih lungput
   a leng (Bawi Khrih lungput a leng) Khrihfa nunning fiang tein a lang.
   (nunning fiang tein a lang).

[V3]
 Bawi Khrih tihzahnak in a khatmi inn, cu inn nuam, inn thluachuak a si
 tawn, Khrihfami nih kan i tinh ciomi cu inn nuam inn thluachuak sinak a
 si.

[C3]
   Bawi Khrih a umnak inn cu (nak inn cu) Inn nuam, inn thluachuak a
   si, Bawi Khrih muihmai a cung, (hmai a cuang zungzal,) Bawi Khrih lungput
   a leng (Bawi Khrih lungput a leng) Khrihfa nunning fiang tein a lang.
   (nunning fiang tein a lang).</lyrics>
</song>